{"tid":2192216,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"流亡手足獲大學取錄 半工讀融入台灣","createTime":"2020-09-07T03:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T05:07:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f5032c5e52b7eada6cd429cb552299ddbaddb3e3","tid":2192216,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:39:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/LGE4CMUBLBEDPFNI2VMX5C7G6M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FLGE4CMUBLBEDPFNI2VMX5C7G6M%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp7Hzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=46b8e461\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FLGE4CMUBLBEDPFNI2VMX5C7G6M%2F&h=41c0db8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/LGE4CMUBLBEDPFNI2VMX5C7G6M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n流亡手足獲大學取錄 半工讀融入台灣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/itpul5gd1VXN7Y6MaGD-11tEQyk=/2099x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FBIFJREGW5EW3M7RRAONZCAIRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fitpul5gd1VXN7Y6MaGD-11tEQyk%3D%2F2099x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFBIFJREGW5EW3M7RRAONZCAIRQ.jpg&h=f618762f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■保護傘分店近日裝修完畢開張試業，店內設有大幅文宣牆。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港府鎮壓反送中運動，大批年輕抗爭者流亡台灣。由香港律師黃國桐發起、讓流亡台灣香港抗爭者工作的保護傘餐廳正式營運後，令更多流亡手足可以在台灣自力更生。有在台手足表示前路亦漸見明朗，有部份人更已收到大學錄取通知，並可繼續工作賺取生活費，減輕照顧他們的「香港家長」負擔之餘，也開始與台灣正常生活慢慢地接軌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「結束方向不定日子」<br />\n<br />\n保護傘餐廳今年4月正式營運，幫助不少在台香港年輕人，流亡台灣的手足輝仔在本報網上論壇撰文直言，保護傘信任在台手足，「就像是給予創業機會，有空間和資源嘗試發揮鈢。。。。<br />\n<br />\n輝仔在文中指，踏入9月後不少流亡台灣手足的前路已漸見明朗，。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n保護傘開分店賣飲品<br />\n<br />\n輝仔又提及保護傘餐廳為繼續支援在台手足，已積極拓展業務，並在餐廳旁邊開設分店保護傘手搖飲料店，主要售賣由手足自創調配的手搖飲品，該店更會讓黃店、手足寄賣自家設計的抗爭產品、二手服飾等，令在台手足可以自食其力、落地生根。<br />\n<br />\n另外保護傘亦有設立網店代購，約十名手足獲聘用，。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0_oU3dGtuqMwNzB1vVkFR0C3rKU=/1181x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RPMZ6TSAQ5FZNPCZNKGYXF5KXA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0_oU3dGtuqMwNzB1vVkFR0C3rKU%3D%2F1181x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRPMZ6TSAQ5FZNPCZNKGYXF5KXA.jpg&h=7945972d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■保護傘分店在餐廳旁邊開設，主要售賣手搖飲品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BvPD5WbBh5ltqdbtim9uBPEiRbw=/1183x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7QQIFBI5LZDKRM733CBHPCEMW4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBvPD5WbBh5ltqdbtim9uBPEiRbw%3D%2F1183x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7QQIFBI5LZDKRM733CBHPCEMW4.jpg&h=cf52810e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■輝仔收到黃店從香港寄來的月餅和明信片。"},{"pid":"71559ba4f950a895a701e3bf0112b28406c1766d","tid":2192216,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:47:41.000Z","msg":"good"},{"pid":"3a071817f82a9775fddff550d06c0ad900b7410e","tid":2192216,"uid":33104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:03:13.000Z","msg":"唔知點解覺得果位律師以加好危險..."},{"pid":"bfd6ce98c6414d8a97c6ef29996fe3392c2bde31","tid":2192216,"uid":350216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fea1d5b998814a1df525ede28d4e6effc8cd8a3","tid":2192216,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:38:26.000Z","msg":"多謝台灣"},{"pid":"4d5835cb5d9886decaa97dbde433c8a8bb2aff45","tid":2192216,"uid":314029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T0